[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0012","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0013","title":"SGI IRIX 6.2 midikeys/soundplayer 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.2 系统中的 midikeys 和 soundplayer 程序存在本地权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在 .wav 文件中嵌入 shell 元字符，当 midikeys 程序处理该恶意音频文件时，soundplayer 会执行其中的 shell 命令，从而使攻击者获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，利用难度较低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0013"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:49.387","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.3 或更高版本以修复 soundplayer/midikeys 程序对 shell 元字符过滤不严的问题。如无法升级，执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/soundplayer /usr/sbin/midikeys` 移除 setuid 位，或限制可执行权限仅授予受信任用户组作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/909","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19706","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a5db9ce197a4914a8237308d958cd159d8832fe6/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0013.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0013","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0013.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0013.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v79x-j3c2-jc67/GHSA-v79x-j3c2-jc67.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0013.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001069.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0012.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0100","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0100.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0043","title":"BroadGun Software CamShot WebCam 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"BroadGun Software 旗下 CamShot WebCam 2.5 的 HTTP 服务器组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务发送超长 GET 请求即可触发缓冲区溢出，进而导致服务崩溃或远程代码执行。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，影响 CamShot WebCam 2.5 版本。目前已有公开的利用代码，建议用户升级至最新版本或停止使用受影响产品。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0043"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:53.007","remediation":"立即停止使用 BroadGun CamShot WebCam 2.5，该产品已停止维护且无安全补丁可用。建议迁移至受支持的网络摄像头方案（如 Axis、Hikvision 等仍在更新中的产品）。若无法立即替换，可在网络边界防火墙或反向代理上限制对 CamShot HTTP 服务的访问，仅允许受信 IP 连接，并配置 WAF 规则拦截超长 GET 请求（超过 4096 字节）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/905","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19702","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6e17eb087fb437c23db93be0dd8d10804be51087/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0043.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0043","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0043.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1eab609178bfac1fdc1fdc37b8b4d17d9ecf98b7/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0043.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gp47-j2wc-phgv/GHSA-gp47-j2wc-phgv.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0043.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000979.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ec3be0baed1eb129c466b944014a0769e187fd54/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0100.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0100.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0062","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0062.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0076","title":"Debian nvi 本地任意文件删除漏洞","description":"Debian 发行版中 nvi 软件包所带的 nviboot 启动脚本存在安全缺陷，该脚本用于在系统启动时恢复 vi 编辑器中意外中断的会话。由于脚本对 vi.recover 目录中的恢复条目缺乏充分的合法性校验，本地已登录的普通用户可通过构造恶意或格式错误的恢复条目，诱使 nviboot 在系统启动或恢复过程中错误地删除根目录（/）下的文件。该漏洞属于本地权限提升/文件破坏类问题，影响范围限于安装了存在缺陷版本 nvi 软件包的 Debian 及其衍生 Linux 系统，攻击前提是攻击者需具备本地账户并能够写入 vi.recover 相关条目。成功利用后可导致系统关键文件被误删，进而引发拒绝服务或系统不稳定，CVSS 基础评分约为 2.1，危害等级较低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0076"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:57.030","remediation":"升级 Debian nvi 软件包至当前已修复版本（bullseye/bookworm 系列为 1.81.6 以上），执行 apt upgrade nvi 安装最新补丁。如无法立即升级，可通过 chmod 700 /var/lib/vi.recover 限制恢复目录权限，或禁用 nviboot 启动脚本来消除 vi.recover 恶意文件触发本地文件删除的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94709988232618&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1439","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/20b9340dcaffca733259fb153ac741206a5bbc5f/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0076.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0076","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0076.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e90735e3e31fc62018265dfbae313d166e653462/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0076.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pxv9-gf47-px56/GHSA-pxv9-gf47-px56.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0076.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/2000/20000108.data","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000980.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0062.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0005","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0003","title":"UnixWare rtpm 程序缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"UnixWare 操作系统自带的 rtpm 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，其在处理环境变量时未对输入长度进行边界校验。本地已登录的普通用户可通过设置超长的环境变量（如向环境传入异常长度的字符串）触发该溢出，覆盖栈上返回地址或相邻内存，从而以 root 等更高权限执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响运行 rtpm 程序的 UnixWare 系统本地用户，攻击前提为攻击者已获得目标系统的本地访问权限，利用方式依赖构造恶意环境变量启动该程序。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0003"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-30","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"厂商已发布补丁修复该漏洞，建议用户升级 UnixWare 至最新版本或安装对应安全补丁。如无法升级，应限制不可信用户对 rtpm 程序的本地访问权限，移除 rtpm 的 setuid 位以降低提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94908470928258&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0099","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0099.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0042","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9115,\"outputTokens\":23,\"totalTokens\":10802}}","description":"CSM 邮件服务器在处理客户端连接时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当远程攻击者与目标邮件服务器建立 SMTP 连接，并在会话初始阶段发送超长的 HELO 命令（包含远超预期长度的字符串）时，服务器未能对输入长度进行边界校验，导致内部缓冲区被溢出覆盖。该漏洞影响运行存在缺陷版本的 CSM 邮件服务器的系统，未经身份认证的远程攻击者无需任何权限即可利用此缺陷，既可使邮件服务崩溃造成拒绝服务，也可能通过精心构造的溢出数据覆盖返回地址，从而在目标服务器上执行任意命令，完全控制受影响主机。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0042"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:52.883","remediation":"建议立即升级 CSM mail server 至官方发布的修复版本（2000 年 1 月补丁版本），并限制 SMTP 服务端口（默认 25）仅对可信 IP 开放。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙或入侵防御系统上设置 HELO 命令长度阈值（如不超过 512 字节），阻断超长 HELO 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/895","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0042.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0612695ef658bcfcb0304f7ee1180b94e9117a85/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0042.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0042","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/2000.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/406e8eff8de253c79b1ce6440b2cb83ff8ecafd4/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0042.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0042.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/smtp.rules","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1350a058fd894925a30c6c0be1a2f33e058296b9/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qh86-6qqc-frf4/GHSA-qh86-6qqc-frf4.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/C/csm_helo.nasl","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.604"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0099.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0084","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0084.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0100","title":"Microsoft Systems Management Server 2.0 默认权限本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Microsoft Systems Management Server 2.0 的远程控制程序在安装时使用了不安全的默认权限设置，导致本地攻击者可以修改或替换该程序文件，从而以系统权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 SMS 2.0 版本，攻击者需要拥有本地访问权限，无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议管理员手动修复文件权限或升级至更高版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0100"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:00.050","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft Systems Management Server 2.0 最新 Service Pack（参见 KB288239），修复远程代理目录权限为 Everyone Full Control 的问题。如无法立即更新，可卸载或禁用 SMS 远程控制功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/current/0045.html","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-012","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19728","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0100.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0100","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0100.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cdbbe57bd34c799f670485304ef54912650bf03b/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0100.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-693g-pv65-m2gh/GHSA-693g-pv65-m2gh.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0100.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000976.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0084.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0010","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0010.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0009","title":"Nortel Networks Optivity NETarchitect 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Nortel Networks Optivity NETarchitect 2.0 中的 bna_pass 程序存在不安全的环境变量调用漏洞。该程序在执行 rm 命令时直接依赖 PATH 环境变量来定位可执行文件路径，而非使用绝对路径。本地攻击者可通过修改 PATH 环境变量，将恶意程序放置在搜索路径中优先于系统 rm 程序被调用，从而以 bna_pass 程序的权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Optivity NETarchitect 2.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0009"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:48.877","remediation":"修改 bna_pass 程序源码，将调用 rm 命令处改为绝对路径 /bin/rm，避免依赖 PATH 环境变量查找可执行文件。如无法修改源码，可移除 bna_pass 的 setuid/setgid 权限位（chmod u-s /path/to/bna_pass），或限制仅受信任的管理员用户可执行该程序。鉴于该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至替代网络管理方案并隔离老旧系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/907","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19704","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0009.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0009","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0009.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0009.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3ch7-w6x4-f69f/GHSA-3ch7-w6x4-f69f.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0009.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000973.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/27329332eaf6d7802a105e6a6dc78246a75b7339/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0010.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0010.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0010.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0008","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0008.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0007","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10786,\"outputTokens\":25,\"totalTokens\":10811}}","description":"Trend Micro PC-Cillin 6.0 内部代理端口未做访问限制，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可直接访问该端口并向其发送特制请求，从而触发拒绝服务攻击，导致该防病毒软件的防护服务中断。该漏洞影响运行 Trend Micro PC-Cillin 6.0 的系统，攻击者无需任何凭据即可在远程完成利用，进而影响主机的安全防护能力。建议用户升级至 Trend Micro 官方发布的安全版本，并参考厂商公告配置防火墙规则限制对内部代理端口的访问，以降低被攻击的风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0007"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:48.623","remediation":"升级 Trend Micro PC-Cillin 至官方发布的 6.02 及以上修复版本，该版本已对内部代理端口增加访问控制限制；如暂时无法升级，可在边界防火墙或本地防火墙规则中禁止外部网络访问 PC-Cillin 所用内部代理端口（默认 TCP 12345），仅允许本机回环地址 127.0.0.1 访问，以阻断远程攻击者发起的拒绝服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1740","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/4491","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/84f82928c38b4d0e02149dbde07f5affc7f46f43/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0007.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0007","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0007.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2a1a519e4e9d3e489c2169e3db04269b559dd18e/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0007.json","https://github.com/stg-tud/cveenhance/blob/6476e73d87cdc9cf610342ef15d131432ab41588/Annotations/Wollny/CVE-2000-0007.xml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mh88-2q4r-3gq4/GHSA-mh88-2q4r-3gq4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0007.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0008.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0037","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0037.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0041","title":"Apple Mac OS 9 ICMP 畸形数据包放大拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Mac OS 9 系统在处理畸形数据包时，会生成超大的 ICMP 响应数据包，攻击者可利用该特性将系统作为中继放大源，发起分布式拒绝服务（DDoS）攻击。具体而言，未经身份认证的远程攻击者通过向目标 Mac OS 9 系统发送精心构造的畸形数据包，即可触发系统返回远大于请求数据包大小的 ICMP 响应，从而实现流量放大，消耗目标网络带宽。该漏洞影响运行 Mac OS 9 的 Macintosh 计算机，攻击条件简单，仅需网络可达且系统启用 ICMP 响应即可利用，可能导致网络服务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0041"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:52.757","remediation":"升级到 Apple 当前支持的 macOS 版本（macOS 15 Sequoia 或更高版本），Mac OS 9 已停止安全更新超过二十年，无法通过补丁修复此漏洞。在防火墙或路由器上配置入站 ICMP 报文速率限制，丢弃来自外部网络的 ICMP 超时报文，临时缓解 ICMP 放大攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/890","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0612695ef658bcfcb0304f7ee1180b94e9117a85/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0041.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0041","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0041.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/406e8eff8de253c79b1ce6440b2cb83ff8ecafd4/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0041.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b41cc7eb86fc3b73b25a431a24646e5a28e1f90/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xvrg-83h8-x5v4/GHSA-xvrg-83h8-x5v4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/2000/CVE-2000-0041.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_100_200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f6072b43-42b8-498b-8bf1-55941fa1ac81.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/CWE-Expert/blob/f634e911e6c24a1ad8b9619383e2ab3eb2d9ebd4/CWE_corpus/markdown/4_cwe_trimmed_top25.md.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0037.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0032","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0032.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0035","title":"Great Circle Associates Majordomo 1.94.4 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Great Circle Associates 开发的 Majordomo 邮件列表管理软件 1.94.4 版本中存在命令注入漏洞。resend 命令在处理用户输入时未正确过滤 shell 元字符，导致拥有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过构造包含特殊字符的恶意请求，以 Majordomo 进程权限执行任意系统命令，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危，受影响系统需升级至修复版本或限制本地用户对 resend 命令的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0035"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:52.027","remediation":"建议立即升级 Majordomo 至 2.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复 resend 命令的 shell 元字符注入问题。如无法升级，需在 resend 脚本中对用户输入严格过滤 shell 元字符（;、`、$、|、& 等），并限制仅管理员可执行 resend 命令。对于 SCO Skunkware 用户，可访问 http://www.sco.com/skunkware 获取更新版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94780294009285&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/902","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19698","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5546763f2cbf8b9d0a5bd1b009f21d50c3edeb8b/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0035.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0035","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0035.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1eab609178bfac1fdc1fdc37b8b4d17d9ecf98b7/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0035.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4wrx-2682-w227/GHSA-4wrx-2682-w227.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/902/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0035.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ec3be0baed1eb129c466b944014a0769e187fd54/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0032.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0013","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0013.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0014","title":"Savant Web Server 空字符拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Savant Web Server 2.0 存在空字符拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者通过在请求 URL 中插入空字符（NULL），可导致 Web 服务器服务崩溃或停止响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Michael Lamont Savant Web Server 2.0 版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，利用方式简单，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0014"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:49.510","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Savant Web Server 2.0，厂商已停止维护且无安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx）。若无法迁移，可在反向代理或 WAF 层面添加规则，拦截包含空字节（%00）的 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/897","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19695","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a5db9ce197a4914a8237308d958cd159d8832fe6/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0014.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0014","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0014.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0014.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pjmx-hxgh-3g67/GHSA-pjmx-hxgh-3g67.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0014.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/27329332eaf6d7802a105e6a6dc78246a75b7339/2000.tsv","https://github.com/c2siorg/bug-connector/blob/68c960cc01a4f61c238e8a780d2247db700d4a9b/Datasets/Mapped_CVE_file.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0013.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0035","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0035.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0037","title":"Majordomo 1.94.4/1.94.5 wrapper 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Majordomo 1.94.4及1.94.5版本的wrapper程序存在本地权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者可通过指定-C参数加载恶意配置文件，从而以Majordomo运行用户的权限执行任意命令，获取系统敏感信息或进一步提权。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0037"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-28","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级Majordomo至已修复版本，或应用Red Hat官方补丁RHSA-2000-005。限制本地用户对wrapper程序的访问权限，避免使用-C参数加载未授权的配置文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T22:21:58.144504587+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94780294009285&w=2","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2000-005.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/903"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0035.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0049","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0049.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0060","title":"aVirt Rover POP3 服务器缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"aVirt Rover POP3 服务器 1.1 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送超长用户名参数触发该漏洞，导致服务器进程崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行 aVirt Rover POP3 server 1.1 的邮件服务器系统，攻击者只需连接到服务器的 POP3 端口（110）并在 USER 命令中传入特制超长字符串即可使服务不可用。由于该服务器是早期流行的 POP3 服务程序，存在该版本的系统均面临被拒绝服务攻击的风险。建议升级至最新版本或更换更安全的 POP3 服务软件以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0060"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:55.140","remediation":"建议升级 aVirt Rover POP3 服务器至官方已修复的后续版本（如 1.2 及以上），或停用存在漏洞的 POP3 服务。作为临时缓解措施，可在防火墙/边界设备上限制仅允许受信任 IP 访问 110 端口，并部署入侵检测规则拦截超长 USER 命令以防范拒绝服务攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94633851427858&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94647711311057&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/3765.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/894","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0060.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0060","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0060.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cf6074d8ac2128dee0a2ac26c5f652ae6527df79/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0060.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g8vp-2x9f-c28w/GHSA-g8vp-2x9f-c28w.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0060.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6d3bebdf-cd32-441f-b7b7-366c34e35544.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0049.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0033","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0033.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0012","title":"Hughes Technologies Mini SQL (mSQL) w3-msql 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Hughes Technologies Mini SQL (mSQL) 2.0.11 的 w3-msql CGI 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 mSQL 2.0.11 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，成功利用后可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0012"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:49.253","remediation":"立即升级 mSQL 至 3.0 及以上版本（当前最新为 4.4），该漏洞在后续版本中已修复。如无法升级，直接删除或禁用 w3-msql CGI 程序（位于 cgi-bin 目录），并在 Web 服务器配置中禁止对该脚本的外部访问。同时限制 Web 服务器以非 root 权限运行，降低缓冲区溢出被利用后的影响范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/898","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19696","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a5db9ce197a4914a8237308d958cd159d8832fe6/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0012.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0012","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0012.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0012.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hcm2-6gpf-h67g/GHSA-hcm2-6gpf-h67g.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0012.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/w3msql_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0033.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0033.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0033.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0030","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0030.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0033","title":"趋势科技 InterScan VirusWall SMTP 邮件扫描绕过漏洞","description":"Trend Micro InterScan VirusWall 的 SMTP 邮件扫描组件存在安全绕过漏洞。该组件在处理带有畸形附件（malformed attachments）的电子邮件时，未能正确解析并扫描邮件内容，导致恶意附件可绕过病毒检测引擎直接投递至收件人。影响范围为部署了 InterScan VirusWall SMTP 扫描功能的产品版本。攻击条件为：远程攻击者只需向受保护邮件域发送一封包含特制畸形附件的 SMTP 邮件，无需身份认证或本地访问权限。利用方式上，攻击者可构造附件边界、编码或结构异常的邮件，使扫描器解析失败或跳过检测，从而将包含病毒、木马或其他恶意载荷的邮件成功绕过防护网关。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0033"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:51.807","remediation":"立即升级 Trend Micro InterScan VirusWall 至最新补丁版本，或安装 Trend Micro 官方发布的 MIME 解析修复补丁。升级后配置 SMTP 扫描器启用严格 MIME 头部验证模式，对包含畸形 Content-Type、边界字符串不匹配或编码异常的邮件附件进行拦截并拒绝投递。临时缓解措施：在邮件网关层面增加对畸形 MIME 结构邮件的深度包检测规则，禁止接收 Content-Transfer-Encoding 与实际情况不符的附件，同时启用邮件内容过滤策略对压缩包及可执行文件附件强制解压扫描。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/899","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2e66cc19cc703324c2947fd6e7687a8b094f9fa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0033.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0033","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0033.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0f6f0e28732bc614273e91613aef04def1dce90b/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0033.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/c137f5e2e6bb5d0d49e919ecf3efde0b10d9a781/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4gxc-2493-86w6/GHSA-4gxc-2493-86w6.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0033.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/1ce7733f932f80d2d4df256d45a61d5d72cee6c8/2000.tsv","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-2000.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0030.toml"}]